<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Yeah right Fabian. Rubbish. Enchanters get hit, and they get hit a lot. No way of avoiding that if you want to play your class properly. If you can't take a couple of rounds of double attacks while you're getting the pull under control you're useless to the group. That's why AC is so important to enchanters (along with having a decent cleric around). This necklace might be useful to a wiz who spends most of the time sitting on his botty, but it would be suicide for an enchanter.</font></td></tr></table>
