<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Verfluken</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-25 21:55:45</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>In answer to the question, you would die if you put this on when you had less than 100 hp.  Believe me, it happened to me when I had less than 55 and I took off my platinum fire opal ring.  To the comment about enchanters taking hits and its suicide to wear this, rubbish.  If you really need ac that badly, this is a great item to free up your fingers for some ac rings, just like the earlier post said, free up enough for 10 ac and 10 bonus hp.  Do the math people, if done right this is the best necklace you could possibly have.</font></td></tr></table>
